WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
Some days, diabetes feels like a full-time job.

00:06.000 --> 00:15.000
Numbers, meals, meds, appointments, supplies, feet, sleep, stress. It's a lot.

00:15.000 --> 00:23.000
So here's the win for today. Pick one thing you can make easier tomorrow.

00:23.000 --> 00:34.000
Refill the meter strips. Put socks by your shoes. Write down your last A1C. Prep the snack. Set the reminder. Ask that question.

00:34.000 --> 00:41.000
Diabetes is daily — so the wins can be daily, too.

00:41.000 --> 00:49.000
Small. Simple. Repeatable.

00:49.000 --> 00:57.000
Diabetes is a 24/7 job. You don't have to carry it alone.

00:57.000 --> 01:04.000
LocalDiabetic. We just help you carry the day. Win big.
